snippet.title: SOCK IT 1.3 - SAGE Trailer
snippet.description:
Play a new and improved build of Sock It at SAGE, the Sonic Amateur Games Expo! It starts on September 4th (https://sagexpo.org), but you can also play the demo now elsewhere!

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1957430/Sock_It/
Itch: https://powerupt.itch.io/sock-it-demo

Many aspects have been improved since Next Fest, it's never been so polished! Check it out!
